{"tid":1852624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！義工聯盟購10萬口罩今抵港　免費派予綜援戶","createTime":"2020-01-30T13:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T17:11:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff62704036ff1a5fe2f546594390f6f0dbadad4","tid":1852624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"與武漢肺炎相關的新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，市面口罩「一罩難求」。香港義工聯盟今日（30日）表示，動用千萬元購入防疫用品，免費派發給有需要的基層市民。首批10萬個防護口罩今晚送抵香港，聯盟將於網上供有需要市民申領，並在港九新界區指定地點派發，綜援戶家庭及長者優先，詳情日內公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/428177/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E8%B3%BC10%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B4%BE%E4%BA%88%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E6%88%B6-%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F428177%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%25B3%25BC10%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25BA%2588%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%2588%25B6-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5784e28e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/428177/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E8%B3%BC10%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B4%BE%E4%BA%88%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E6%88%B6-%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85</a>"},{"pid":"e417d3247126985eb634963be9d71123b9846691","tid":1852624,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"